Package com.cafean.utils.jobstream

Class LocalStageMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.utils.jobstream.LocalStageMapping
  • public class LocalStageMapping
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class used to map a platform staging location to a local file system location.
